# Copy to `.npmrc` in this repo root (`.npmrc` is gitignored).
# Obtain an npm identity token from WEX Artifactory / JFrog (same access as cxr-ux / benefits npm).
#
#   cp .npmrc.example .npmrc
#   export ARTIFACTORY_NPM_TOKEN="YOUR_TOKEN"
#   npm install
#
# Token: Artifactory → user menu → Edit profile → Generate an Identity Token (or your team’s documented API key flow).

@wexinc-healthbenefits:registry=https://usartifactorywexinc.jfrog.io/artifactory/api/npm/benefits-npm/
//usartifactorywexinc.jfrog.io/artifactory/api/npm/benefits-npm/:_authToken=${ARTIFACTORY_NPM_TOKEN}
//usartifactorywexinc.jfrog.io/artifactory/api/npm/benefits-npm/:always-auth=true
